      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.033333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、私は\nLizNoirにいなくてもいい子なんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew I was a ………\nmember who doesn't need to be in LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.233333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん。SNSの活用は俺が言い出したことだ\n愛に自信を持ってもらいたくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ the SNS thing was my idea.\nI wanted to give Ai confidence………",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですよ！　こんな私のために\n何十本も動画を撮って、編集してくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay!\nWe took dozens of videos and you edited them all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "私、芸能界に入ってこんなに良くしてもらったの\n初めてかもしれません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think this may be the first time I've been treated\nso well in the entertainment industry…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "短かったですけど\n最後に星見プロに所属出来て良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a short time‚\nbut I am glad to have belonged to Hoshimi Productions in the end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり今日のライブを最後に\n引退するつもりなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you still planning to retire\nafter today's live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.833333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、LizNoirのみんなの足を\n引っ張りたくないですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ and I don't want to drag\neveryone in LizNoir down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "それにこれ以上、{user}さんにも\n負担はかけられないです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I can't burden {user}-san\nany more than I already have ………",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "愛はそれで本当にいいのか？\nLizNoirに憧れてたんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is Ai really okay with that?\nYou've always had a thing for LizNoir‚ haven't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "好きだからこそ、大事にしたいんです……\nLizNoirは頂点に立てる凄いグループなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like it and I want to take care of it……….\nLizNoir is an amazing group that can be at the top of its game!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんのストイックな姿勢……\n葵さんの自由自在なダンス……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san's stoic attitude………\nAoi-san's graceful dance moves……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "こころの明るくて面白いMC……\nきっと、あの三人ならBIG4にだって勝てます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro's lively and entertaining MC skills………\nSurely‚ with those three‚ they can even surpass the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、俺もあの三人には可能性を感じているよ\nでも、三人のLizNoirじゃBIG4には勝てない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I see a lot of potential in those three‚ too.\nBut three LizNoirs can't beat the BIG 4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしてですか！？\nあの三人の才能を認めてるって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Why?\nYou said you recognizes the talents of those three ………",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
