      "text": "ああ、悪いとは思ったけど、愛の気持ちを\n他のメンバーに伝えて、意見を聞いてみた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm sorry‚ but I told the other members\nand asked their opinions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.23333333333333
