    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　だ、大事なライブの前なのに……\n私、今日、終わったら自分で言うつもりだったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehhh?　It's before an important live……….\nSo I was going to tell them myself when it's done………",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん今日のライブは大切だ。だからこそ\nライブ前に、四人の気持ちを一つにしてほしかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course today's live is important.\nThat's why I wanted the four of you to unite your feelings before the live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
