      "text": "莉央さん、葵、それにこころが俺に託してくれた\n愛への手紙だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ Aoi‚ and Kokoro entrusted it to me.\nThis is for you‚ Ai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺が口で伝えるよりいいと思って、書いてもらったよ\n読んでみてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it was better than me telling you orally‚ so I had them write it down.\nGo ahead. Read them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
