      "text": "愛へ。貴方がそんな風に悩んでるなんて知らなかったわ\n今まで気づいてあげられなくてごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dear Ai. I had no idea you were so troubled.\nI’m sorry I didn’t notice your suffering.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.76666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "愛は私達にないまっすぐな素直さと情熱を持っているわ\nそれは少し屈折した私にはない、とても貴重なものよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have honesty and passion I simply can’t match.\nIt’s something that’s incredibly valuable for someone jaded like me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "技術は教えられても情熱は本人が生まれ持ったものなの\nあなたの情熱がLizNoirには必要なのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Technique can be taught‚ but passion comes from within.\nLizNoir needs your passion!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
