      "text": "愛は絶対これからもっとうまくなれる。本当だよ\n僕はウソと骨の多い魚は大嫌いなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can make it work‚ Ai. I mean it.\nI hate lies as much as I hate bony fishes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai025.m4a",
      "text": "今日は最高のステージにしよう。これからもよろしく\n井川葵……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s make this an incredible live. I’m counting on you.\nAoi Igawa….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
