      "text": "こころは、えっと……愛、こころに\n黙って何勝手なことしようとしてるのーっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro’s letter. Let’s see…. Dear Ai.\nWhy are you sneaking around behind my back?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
