      "text": "愛がいなくなったら、私が失言した時、誰に\n責任を押し付ければいいんですかーっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who’s going to hold me accountable for all the\ndumb stuff I say if you aren’t around?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.3333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
