      "text": "ただでさえ莉央さんにしょっちゅうお目玉もらってる\nこころの防波堤にこれからもなって下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san already scolds me all the time.\nYou must continue to be a sheild of Kokoro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 272.53333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai030.m4a",
      "text": "もし愛が辞めたら、呪います！　夜中に神社で藁人形\nをもってお百度参りです！　ダメ！　辞めたらダメ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll curse you if you quit. I’ll get a voodoo doll\nand prick it with pins and needles! I’ll do it! So no quitting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.8333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
