      "text": "愛の笑顔は、こころの次に素敵です！　自信持って！\n早く二人でLizNoirのど真ん中に立ちましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your smile is second only to mine. Be confident!\nLet’s hurry up and take center stage of LizNoir together!",
        "id": ""
