      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai034.m4a",
      "text": "……こころ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Kokoro….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.1333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 323.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "愛、君は今の自分に自信がないみたいだけど\n周囲はみんな君を認めてる。いや、必要としているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ you might not have confidence in yourself.\nBut everyone else sees what you can do. They need you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 327.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "それを俺はどうしても、君に分かってほしかった\nだから、どうか引退は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what I wanted you to understand.\nPlease‚ can we put this talk of quitting—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 338.3666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 340.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai035.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 340.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai036.m4a",
      "text": "これからも、ご迷惑をおかけしますが\nよろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks like I’ll be causing you\nmore trouble in the future!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 348.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 350.46666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "――えっ？　じゃあ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Does that mean—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.46666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 352.8666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai037.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　みんなの手紙を読んで目が覚めました！\n私、やっぱりLizNoirのメンバーでいたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! These letters opened my eyes!\nI’m a member of LizNoir after all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 357.26666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 361.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai038.m4a",
      "text": "端っこでもいいので莉央さん、葵さん、それにこころと\nアイドルを続けたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I can be an idol with Rio-san‚ Aoi-san‚ and Kokoro‚\nthen I don’t care if I’m in the corner!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 366.3666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 368.46666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
