      "text": "みなさん、こんばんはー！\nLizNoirの新メンバー小美山愛です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good evening everyone!\nI’m Ai Komiyama‚ one of the new members of LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 391.96666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_03-ai042.m4a",
      "text": "ずっとずっと憧れてたLizNoirに加入出来て\n私は、一つの夢を叶えました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve looked up to LizNoir for so long\nthat it’s a dream come true to join them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 399.96666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
